# 💫 About Me: I'm a passionate developer with a focus on building scalable, production-ready systems for startups. With expertise in both the MERN stack and Spring Boot framework, I have successfully delivered multiple projects that are live and driving results for businesses today. Recently, I had the honor of winning Asia’s Largest Blockchain Hackathon – ETH India 22.
